{"tid":980621,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[字海] 我大老師失蹤兩年你問我答","createTime":"2019-01-13T15:58:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T06:17:52.000Z","uid":28823,"like":3,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"24bc6a3eeb7c085a4223e696e9eff4c031dfa5f0","tid":980621,"uid":28823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T15:58:14.000Z","msg":"依兩年無乜接觸ACG，成個人生真係痛苦左好多...<br />\n講返依兩年我做左D咩，方便你地問我野吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1.  無去maid cafe、event、買figure、睇coser<br />\n2.  儲左50萬<br />\n3.  每日訓4-5個鐘<br />\n4. 朋友圈由7個圈子 變到  3個圈子<br />\n5. 比女表白有 16次左右，撩扑野人數好似有8件<br />\n6. A0處<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n7. 無一日開心過<br />\n8. 每日都想係張床到訓教<br />\n9. 好想搵返當年接觸ACG果時興奮感，每日都開心既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10. 發覺人越大真係越空虛啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a184cc9df6e76596c3273817002f16f6cc356bf1","tid":980621,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T15:59:32.000Z","msg":"鋸扒唔能有聲"},{"pid":"f09b82aa34372a27eb9aad24afd26fc9ba40a687","tid":980621,"uid":28823,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a184cc9df6e76596c3273817002f16f6cc356bf1","tid":980621,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T15:59:32.000Z","msg":"鋸扒唔能有聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T16:01:51.000Z","msg":"問D問題可唔可以正常D<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2703c05f5b0559ba7ff728d4153c490dcd30da5f","tid":980621,"uid":58038,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T16:02:47.000Z","msg":"無野問呀 躝啦"},{"pid":"12684cf8dd27bf3a239f12e839f15fd59ac228ba","tid":